{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they wrote me a letter that, while we are not your uncle, we want to help you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you are not related to us, but we want to send you an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We have three children of our own, and we want you to come and be our daughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So practically like by return mail, they send me the papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, it wasn't enough for the American console.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed in Austria quite a number of years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during this time, he wrote me the most beautiful letters, which kept my spirits-- sent me food packages and clothing, and just maintain my spirits, like no one else.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For some reason-- I was an orphan and a minor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with all the documents and everything else, we went, even my aunt and I, undertook the trip to go to the American console general in Naples.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they refused a visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't immigrate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This, to this date, will be something I will never understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And indeed, I'm not a bitter person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when I think that [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Castro ?] is opening his jail and lets people in, and here, after the war, I had to be in a DP camp and not to be let in-- and especially in view of the fact that somebody guaranteed my upkeep-- I cannot ever understand.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I never did come to the States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to Canada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was taken to a transport to Canada, as a domestic, and emigrated to Canada.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1949.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My Aunt Rose, in the meantime, stayed on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only young girls were needed and wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She stayed behind, in Italy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said she would eventually follow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was very hard to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
